rameters like `T create(@Assisted String name)`. Using `@Assisted` on the constructor could simplify things, especially regarding duplicate keys. I also wonder if I should create a package-private or private nested interface `GenericFactory<T>`, and since Java 9 allows private interfaces, it seems permissible. However, I need to confirm if `Proxy.newProxyInstance` can support these private interfaces and how public access affects the proxy's classification.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating metadata generation**\\n\\nI’m thinking about how Forge metadata generation will be handled. The existing proxy test covers the package-private `LegacyWidgetFactory`, and it looks like the metadata is being generated correctly, which is great! I need to ensure that `MethodHandles.publicLookup()` is recognized as a public API in a natural way. That seems straightforward enough, but I want to double-check everything to make sure there are no hiccups in the process.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_pXiZanjDkVeJLRfSHH7St5xk|fc_032f4579d02ec6840169fd6ca18c4c819dbab0f92e372bd985", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/com.google.inject.extensions/guice-assistedinject/6.0.0/src/test/java/com_google_inject_extensions/guice_assistedinject/FactoryProvider2InnerPrivateLookupTest.java", "content": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage com_google_inject_extensions.guice_assistedinject;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\n\nimport com.google.inject.AbstractModule;\nimport com.google.inject.Guice;\nimport com.google.inject.Inject;\nimport com.google.inject.Injector;\nimport com.google.inject.assistedinject.Assisted;\nimport com.google.inject.assistedinject.FactoryModuleBuilder;\nimport java.lang.invoke.MethodHandles;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\npublic class FactoryProvider2InnerPrivateLookupTest {\n    @Test\n    void fallsBackToPrivateLookupForGeneratedBridgeDefaultMethod() {\n        Injector injector = Guice.createInjector(new AbstractModule() {\n            @Override\n            protected void configure() {\n                bind(BridgeSuffixService.class).toInstance(new BridgeSuffixService(\"-bridge\"));\n                install(new FactoryModuleBuilder()\n                        .withLookups(MethodHandles.publicLookup())\n                        .build(BridgeWidgetFactory.class));\n            }\n        });\n\n        BridgeWidgetFactory factory = injector.getInstance(BridgeWidgetFactory.class);\n        BridgeWidget directWidget = factory.create(\"direct\");\n        GenericBridgeFactory<BridgeWidget> genericFactory = factory;\n        BridgeWidget genericWidget = genericFactory.create(\"generic\");\n\n        assertThat(directWidget.description()).isEqualTo(\"direct-bridge\");\n        assertThat(genericWidget.description()).isEqualTo(\"generic-bridge\");\n    }\n\n    private interface GenericBridgeFactory<T> {\n        T create(@Assisted String name);\n    }\n\n    private interface BridgeWidgetFactory extends GenericBridgeFactory<BridgeWidget> {\n        @Override\n        BridgeWidget create(@Assisted String name);\n    }\n\n    static final class BridgeWidget {\n        private final BridgeSuffixService suffixService;\n        private final String name;\n\n        @Inject\n        BridgeWidget(BridgeSuffixService suffixService, @Assisted String name) {\n            this.suffixService = suffixService;\n            this.name = name;\n        }\n\n        String description() {\n            return name + suffixService.value();\n        }\n    }\n\n    static final class BridgeSuffixService {\n        private final String value;\n\n        BridgeSuffixService(String value) {\n            this.value = value;\n        }\n\n        String value() {\n            return value;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1950, "output": 1157, "cacheRead": 23552, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26659, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778216083793, "responseId": "resp_032f4579d02ec6840169fd6c944bc0819da4bbb122b47b9e2e"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_pXiZanjDkVeJLRfSHH7St5xk|fc_032f4579d02ec6840169fd6ca18c4c819dbab0f92e372bd985", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2580 bytes to tests/src/com.google.inject.extensions/guice-assistedinject/6.0.0/src/test/java/com_google_inject_extensions/guice_assistedinject/FactoryProvider2InnerPrivateLookupTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778216099445}]}
