sts or library reachability. It seems like the user-code-filter is critical here, as it determines which classes are included as \"user code\" for the conditional configuration in the Graal agent.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_032f4579d02ec6840169fd6e435ddc819db1521b2f666029c5\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_W5ZJMY_iNOqJWnctkgfWRY23cRjXzWTMC7gnquake6n1anYCSh4itfzGG3rNhiIwd7Q6zd6EyzEQVSvxt3xHmQOXsd0DcsK-FYp5dQ1QIq4a1DyrbQ3fzV4x6Srun0Qepd0I8bzFvJYGjmcx-NcX9tN1mtvgQpR8GO4yRLxkBtI8NicZiYvpfdOD8jXJSZk69KsUeEP3GjyeDxvXN-yQTv_ShJS4Qd80vy9IGzM_B6tdhdfvqjO11NZOX4KIwN_ntyY-28HxR1q-GIBVTgb43UvfWPTEFEDbkM0EsefA8d0wy1ZJt2TiDUTCNKgXdUR15lstwsLZcX6JDpXIvaxkycAnjQPCY8WpsgTqWCwHDPmcv2LjCUaKFGdxilmMqDhFFhdWCSoe0U71envZHsAi1R6S2sRpwj-8bq5ePtLnhG754TLUd8QpAtyO-U6P0B-icW7ytDQ_3qWfDuDT5eld-ZwuaChrgRahVqAuyTvClmXTZ2jJQUuTxcwyTzTXtlCqdShzqLOEPcLEQ-dRrmqJMC3GLoAqGotmCayqxUI_frYU7P81wb6k3xkXNLa9l2i9fR54PY1KsNXfXKQEKyz1JONHgCjSHs2wTQ_kbICeP6F17aI5ODAnIPn8ALSx5SNQX1Zj6jJ2OMivUpATqoh2eA1-sHLjz4wKfASYEDBF3obyS7100dUtI9xtqeLgGiFUdzZju5zisoKFttc0plVlfcevC2R5jn_2c_QuyhaZjiERXNSxR3_q7YPEdTIMQmba38_9Hwlf-RhfQ7If5DzeHfBmbm-GiCKTs8VrgbVzQ717HTE6DIYXd4gzMopJSxQx9x-_p-pZ8OMhL8e7pFO0LE26PB5k2pBbEe-7KKMfEYzWYGvmhzY_joiikFjgepBzeeHwqPVcbfexzi64D0DY4MiLw9UStpJMgBJhRrulRIZvgd8O52iK0HCVO7HPHvfVKkQF565drdR_lQ6A3_mxcpyqAaRaTtwz9YTbya0lnMEtgZFtrxsYYyxSMNay3AVo3UYL5JVXT2zsSm9MTdliaNW5x4b5MRM7tUecIt_soYq4W4fo0sUzVgOGZbmkxJlIlyiR5KdgSugaZCiRTLdinPyjEQCLDmC28uRxE8bISd1yh4Mx5eZ6C5hYxuIwUwubzA4NAaXAnge6qY6irft9wZRPdaXv9gWb5kPOjK4md5qSDWKX6MJJ06okPNt5wCxuq7XOMk6qRbbgf-PKreodmkgKCE3S51NzSpaqgcwWyR1VAYuHSd3tPuU0Hz4XTlLZ0U1LFN1u3WLg6-TR0pbMqu47nAQftFAftSZ1YbL0Psbf2KGqW7srHGd5bgwdMCodKdISQMnCScrOd6TQEXtXTWCY-0-0Le26QIynF671RrrP7Tjg9-dtBst6vMnoE9rtapF0kWFSvO4AsTDakRTpoHgCqaZmYQjun40tH5TJUH4sLItZ2hvyO-UcKJVM20JlgZ6tzFWMcKQJD_CgMu03dLfaO6lYyG0EYoDobwjcq6sjj0ilg4qxSZWx84dSRpRFhLYyya4myAPUZScnE8JvXArGj547Df4di4hoEFIc-_Ru_StbMr02Zu4otMqpdNBLQ0X4ai5ShF3P7FKm2pA0k6-Bgf4_alHWV_ibNKK1hLj516rn0ax6s9Axs